# PowerEdge R740 (gen 14, 2U dual-socket, iDRAC9).
#
# UNTESTED — gen 14 introduced iDRAC9 with a new BMC firmware lineage.
# Behavior likely similar to gen 13 (clamps low PWM to safety RPM)
# but not verified. Default MIN_FAN=20 is conservative pending probe.
#
# Probe before lowering — see r720.env for procedure. If R740 BMC
# clamps like R730xd, MIN_FAN=10 is safe.

: "${MIN_FAN:=20}"
